01:15:28,362 --> 01:15:32,699
In Brixton today, a sensational
murder trial was concluded.

952
01:15:32,783 --> 01:15:35,410
Donald J. Barksdale
was found guilty...

953
01:15:35,494 --> 01:15:38,622
in the sex and strangulation
killing of Jessica King,

954
01:15:38,705 --> 01:15:43,210
daughter of the prominent Brixton
businessman, Kenneth King.

955
01:15:43,293 --> 01:15:46,380
Is everything gonna be
all right now, Mama?

956
01:15:46,463 --> 01:15:48,882
Yeah, hon.

957
01:15:48,966 --> 01:15:51,677
We can get on
with our lives now.

958
01:16:45,063 --> 01:16:47,399
I guess I'm the last
person you wanna see.

959
01:16:51,278 --> 01:16:53,864
How you been?

960
01:16:57,826 --> 01:16:59,745
Terrible.

961
01:17:01,622 --> 01:17:05,083
